               <p>JOHN TODHUNTER. On the 5th of July, about half-past ten o'clock in the evening, I was walking with a friend in <placeName id="t18260914-452-crimeloc2544">Fleet-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260914-452-crimeloc2544" type="placeName" value="Fleet-street"></interp>
